@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Carrier erstmals anlegen: 201 Created
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/carriers
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicate Name Test",
  "nation": "Germany",
  "carrierType": "AIRCRAFT_CARRIER",
  "commandCenter": {
    "codeName": "First Command",
    "securityLevel": 2
  },
  "aircrafts": []
}

### Denselben Namen erneut anlegen: 409 Conflict
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/carriers
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicate Name Test",
  "nation": "France",
  "carrierType": "HELICOPTER_CARRIER",
  "commandCenter": {
    "codeName": "Second Command",
    "securityLevel": 4
  },
  "aircrafts": []
}
